{
  "stem": "11744.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When you think back on it, did it almost feel like you were just afraid for all the time, for all the years?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Was there always a certain tension in your body?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, there were-- depending where you were and who you were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The French people were-- were less-- were less in danger, but not the Jewish-French.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, the Jews were always in danger, no matter-- no matter where they-- I lost two cousins of mine with four children who tried to pass the line between the free zone to the occupied zone.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted to go back to Paris, and they were picked up by the line and disappeared completely when they-- you just-- the people just went and just disappeared.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You never saw them again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you knew it could happen to you tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was no reason why it shouldn't happen, but you had to be busy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You had to do a lot of things in order to not-- not to think all the time, otherwise you were lost.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it's a-- the more you did, and more activity you had, then better it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was unlivable otherwise.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You didn't have enough food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Didn't have anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
